The paper is about using Arabic Wordnet for semantic indexation in Information Retrieval Systems. This topic falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) as well as Natural Language Processing (cs.CL). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques to improve the performance of the system, which falls under the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Deep Learning (cs.DL).
